## ⚠️ Read before you write code

This project follows a **strict documentation-in-sync discipline** and **enterprise coding
standards**. Before contributing (human or AI):

1. Read **[`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md)** — the working contract (conventions, the after-every-change
   ritual, coding standards, security rules).
2. Read **[`docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md`](docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md)** — enforced limits.
3. Read **[`docs/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md`](docs/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md)** — set up, run, test, branch.

**Golden rule: secrets and cryptographic keys NEVER enter git.** See [`docs/SECURITY.md`](docs/SECURITY.md).

