## Quick start

```bash
cd backend && python -m venv .venv && . .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt -r requirements-dev.txt
uvicorn {{ python_package }}.main:app --reload    # http://localhost:8000/health
cd .. && make check && make dod-check             # the full gate
```

